jasima.core.experiment

接口 ExperimentListener

  • 所有超级接口:
    NotifierListener<Experiment,Experiment.ExperimentMessage>
    所有已知实现类:
    AbstractResultSaver, ConsolePrinter, ExcelSaver, ResultSaver, XmlSaver

    public interface ExperimentListener
extends NotifierListener<Experiment,Experiment.ExperimentMessage>
    This class can be used as a base class for experiment listeners. It delegates all events of Experiment to separate methods.
    作者:
    Torsten Hildebrandt
